Class OmniIndivisibleValue

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Number
javax.money.NumberValue
foundation.omni.OmniValue
foundation.omni.OmniIndivisibleValue
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<NumberValue>
public final class OmniIndivisibleValue extends OmniValue
Numeric Value of Indivisible Omni Token An indivisible token is an integer number of tokens that can't be subdivided to less than one token.
